      • toMessage

        public IFIXMessage toMessage(Object source,
                             IFIXMessage target,
                             boolean dialectAllowNoLengthOnRawData)
                      throws IllegalArgumentException,
                             UnsupportedOperationException,
                             NullPointerException
        Converts the FIX based format contained in the TIBRV message to the object format used by the Catalys Server.
        Specified by:
        toMessage in interface IToMessageTransformer
        Parameters:
        source - The TIBRV message containing the message data.
        target - The message converted to the object-based format used by the Catalys Server.
        dialectAllowNoLengthOnRawData - True to indicate that no special treatment is to be given to raw data and their associated length fields (that is, they are expected to conform to regular FIX field content and in particular the data field should not contain FIX SOH), false to treat the data field as opaque and use its preceding length field to determine its length.
        Returns:
        The message converted to the object-based format used by the Catalys Server.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if there was an error parsing or transforming the message.
        NullPointerException - if target is null
        UnsupportedOperationException - If this form of transformation is not supported by this transformer.

      • toObject

        public Object toObject(IFIXMessage source,
                       Object target)
                throws IllegalArgumentException,
                       UnsupportedOperationException,
                       CryptoException
        Converts the object format used by the Catalys Server to the FIX based format contained in the TIBRV message. Note: StandartFixTransformer ignore 3 fields during transformation - BeginString, BodyLength and TAGiCheckSum
        Specified by:
        toObject in interface IFromMessageTransformer
        Parameters:
        source - A message in the object based format used by the Catalys Server.
        target - The Catalys Server Message converted to the FIX based TIBRV format.
        Returns:
        The Catalys Server Message converted to the FIX based TIBRV format.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - Thrown if an exception occurs while extracting fields from the Catalys Server message or adding a field to the TIBRV message.
        UnsupportedOperationException - if this form of transformation is not supported by this transformer.
        CryptoException - If the transformation failed due to an encryption problem
